{"tid":1845475,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【梁卓偉食屎】專科醫生憂隱形病人已在社區　戴口罩是唯一自保方法","createTime":"2020-01-27T07:37:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T07:40:48.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b83435d3ee30ecd366029d7691ede26cedffa780","tid":1845475,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T07:37:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1505071_1_L_20200127134134.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1505071_1_L_20200127134134.jpg&h=c6024b23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府宣布，凌晨開始，除香港居民外，所有湖北省居民以及任何過去14日到過湖北省人士，不獲准入境香港，直至另行通知，以減低新型冠狀病毒感染者進入香港的機會。<br />\n<br />\n感染及傳染病專科醫生曾祈殷表示，有關措施理應早於大年初一前的一星期或內地春運開始時果斷地實行，擔心很多隱形病人已在社區，呼籲市民外出時配戴口罩，相信是現時唯一能自保的方法。<br />\n<br />\n曾祈殷說，香港是國際城市及交通樞紐，如出現社區爆發，將加劇病毒在世界各地傳播。他認為，入境處有責任與內地聯絡，了解已入境內地旅客過去曾到訪哪些城市，亦要通報醫管局，又建議急症室醫護人員不能盡信病人，不要對聲稱並非來自湖北省的病人掉以輕心，必須穿好保護衣物。<br />\n<br />\n對於有醫護團體可能發起罷工，要求封關阻截更多患者來港。曾祈殷指，醫生有救人的天職，不贊成以工業行動表達訴求，認為應先做好防疫工作，但社會各界亦要向政府施壓，要求正視醫護人員的聲音，作多方面配合。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505071-20200127.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505071-20200127.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=FyFnEhDp3tEmtF3AT420RgRUsGYs0X8VP9vM6mjQjJM%3D&h=c061e4d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505071-20200127.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=78178603\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505071-20200127.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/mask-16_1Aalv_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fmask-16_1Aalv_1200x0.png&h=2eca5d78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/fcwmFJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FfcwmFJ.jpg&h=89b73ac5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b1dc925cc37f5f9f980f389763f14364f037b8de","tid":1845475,"uid":344033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T07:38:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/117867026414155/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F112357283631796%2Fposts%2F117867026414155%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=FyFnEhDp3tEmtF3AT420RgRUsGYs0X8VP9vM6mjQjJM%3D&h=dcbb21f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/117867026414155/?d=n</a><br />\n戴眼罩！"},{"pid":"85db5966ba1a5afec763a76bfa6cf9617929f6dd","tid":1845475,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T07:38:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/mask-16_1Aalv_1200x0.png\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.speakout.hk/articles/cover/20200125/02e57c9dfcfc72f6925bccc44b69cf05.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.speakout.hk%2Farticles%2Fcover%2F20200125%2F02e57c9dfcfc72f6925bccc44b69cf05.jpeg&h=1be08796&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t0Njc9M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft0Njc9M.jpg&h=c0f7d13d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pJYnbM1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpJYnbM1.png&h=55464653&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1aeebd5a8a4b5b3098881e9018cc28434ad0b8ae","tid":1845475,"uid":318300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T07:40:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t0Njc9M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft0Njc9M.jpg&h=c0f7d13d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa